def simple_plot(x, y, title, y_label, xticks_list, x_label='Date'):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))
    plt.plot(x, y, linewidth=0.8, color='red')

    plt.xticks(xticks_list, rotation=45)

    plt.title(title)
    plt.xlabel(x_label)
    plt.ylabel(y_label)

    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
